com.innowhere.jnieasy.core.method
Interface NativeMethodReflection

All Superinterfaces:
CanBeNativeCapable, NativeBehavior, NativeBehaviorReflection, NativeCallback, NativeCapable, NativeFieldContainer, NativeMemberReflection, NativeMethod, NativeMethodCallback, NativeObjectFieldContainer, NativeSingleFieldContainer
All Known Subinterfaces:
NativeInstanceMethodReflection, NativeStaticMethodReflection
public interface NativeMethodReflection
extends NativeBehaviorReflection, NativeMethodCallback

The NativeMethodReflection is the interface implemented by native capable classes that make accessible Java methods from native. Java methods are accessed using Java reflection.

Author:
Jose M. Arranz Santamaria
